title: Finblox: Earn Bitcoin & Crypto

creator: Finblox
descriptionHtml:
Finblox - Supercharge your crypto ⚡

Buy & swap crypto with ease 💸
Easily onboard by depositing or purchasing your favorite cryptos through our partners such as Moonpay, Transak, Xanpool and many more. Or, enjoy our lighting-fast swaps to begin earning yield!

Passive income while you sleep 😴
Earn some of the most competitive APY rates on the market for Bitcoin, Ethereum, USDC, USDT, MATIC, and many others. Plus, up to 15% on stablecoins.

Freedom & accessibility 🕊️
No minimums, no lock-ins - with yields compounded and paid daily. Never wait for payday again!

Win free crypto prizes weekly 🏆
Enter weekly drawings in Pool Party, and boost your chances of winning by taking beneficial actions in our ecosystem.

Security & peace of mind 🔒
Rest well knowing that your funds are in the custody of Fireblocks, the world's most reputable digital assets infrastructure provider. Featuring bank-grade security, encryption, and MPC technology.

Sign up in minutes 💨
Register your Finblox account and pass Identity Verification KYC in a flash. Instantly swap, deposit, or buy crypto to start earning!

Supportive & experienced team 🏋🏻‍♀️
Our team hails from some of the largest and most respected companies in the world, such as Coins.PH (Philippines' largest crypto exchange with 16M+ users), Gotrade (Y-Combinator backed zero-commission investment platform), Lazada, VNG, and Grab.

Backed by top investors 💫
We're backed by an all-star lineup of angels, advisors, and VCs including Sequoia Capital, Dragonfly Capital, MSA, Venturra Discovery, Saison Capital, Coinfund, Cypher Capital, Razer, and many others.

Learn more: www.finblox.com
Contact us: support@finbloxapp.com
